description:
PReset is a Windows-based program for the configuration of programmable devices in the 5000-, 5300-, 5500- and 6300-series for temperature measurement, level measurement, isolation, etc.



PReset version 11.01.1007

New in this version:
- Maintenance release with minor bug fixes and enhancements.

Note: Uninstall old versions of PReset before installing the new version.
